summary: a phan account literally just sent me some awkward, weird pick up lines that would sound creepy if you said them irl, and they...
body:
a phan account literally just sent me some awkward, weird pick up lines that would sound creepy if you said them irl, and they seemed like a joke but then they sounded serious and i started crying with laughter. any other person who doesn’t have a fandom account would be like ‘wtf leave me alone.’…


however we are now friends.


that’s the internet people. amen.
